Camera FrontBack transforms your iPhone into a multi-cam allowing you to capture video from two cameras at the same time.

With our video App, we want people around the world to shoot amazing views, architecture, pets, and friends and at the same time allow them to express their emotions being on one screen. Try and get surprised at how you reacted to something which was important to you at the moment.

Features:
◆ Picture-in-picture (PIP);
◆ Simultaneous work with front and rear cameras;
◆ Animates in real-time;
◆ Circle mode;
◆ Oval mode;
◆ Square mode;
◆ Full-Screen mode;
◆ Split-screen mode;
◆ Pinch-to-zoom;
◆ Capture moment;
◆ Moveable around screen;

it has a user-friendly interface and it's easy to use.

A simple and complete app for self-timer, continuous shooting and selfie, with grills, timer and adjustable intervals! 

Features: 
- Works on iPhone, iPad and iPod touch; 
- Timer first photo, adjustable from 0s to 120s; 
- Multiple shots, adjustable from 1 to 200; 
- Timer for multiple shots in sequence and adjustable from 2s to 120s; 
- Flash on, off, automatic; 
- Turn on the flashlight to illuminate the scene; 
- Beep sound for 5 seconds before each shot (can be disabled); 
- Auto-save in the photo gallery (can be disabled); 
- Three grids to better frame the scene (rule of thirds and the golden section); 
- Automatic recognition of faces; 
- Front and rear camera; 
- Digital Zoom; 
- Focus Automatic or manual; 
- Preview photos in high definition; 
- Share photos on social networks, or with your favorite applications, printing, copying, use as background Wallpaper! 


For information or suggestions, please use the Contact Us form in the Info menu of the application.
